request.description:
This endpoint retrieves a list of students across a specific course.

### Request

- Method: GET
- URL: `localhost:3100/student/across-course/student`

- Body:

    - course_code (string, required): The code of the course for which the students are to be retrieved.

### Response

- Status: 200 OK
- Body:

    ```
        {
            "message": "A message indicating the result of the request",
            "data": [
                {
                    "student": "The name of a student"
                }
            ]
        }

     ```


#### Example Response

``` json
{
    "message": "HERE ARE THE STUDENTS OFFERING ENG400",
    "data": [
        {
            "student": "Jumo1"
        },
        {
            "student": "Jumo1"
        }
    ]
}

 ```

